Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.56,0:12:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.58,0:13:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我竟然会在地板上睡着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.65,0:13:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个完美无暇的美貌才是我的终极之道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.29,0:13:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.12,0:13:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要保持充足睡眠才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.36,0:13:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美里同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.43,0:13:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道睡着了没？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.54,0:13:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,睡觉的样子也好可爱喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.39,0:13:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个洗衣板女佣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.83,0:14:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.25,0:14:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(给阿优)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.39,0:14:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给阿优
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.26,0:14:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.06,0:14:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为事发突然 不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.23,0:14:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我因为某些缘故 必须到远方去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.77,0:14:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时间虽然短暂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.50,0:14:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但与阿优相处的这段时光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.87,0:14:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得非常的幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.94,0:14:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你至今的照顾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.38,0:14:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.15,0:14:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻幌上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.99,0:14:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.22,0:14:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我没有发现呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.07,0:15:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻幌呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.80,0:15:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她说要去决斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.29,0:15:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,子弹用完了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.93,0:15:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这边好像也用得差不多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.87,0:15:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来孤注一掷 赌输赢的时候似乎到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.11,0:15:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.51,0:15:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻幌到底去哪里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.68,0:15:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点告诉我呀 史莱修
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.38,0:15:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 我答应麻幌 不能告诉你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.12,0:16:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且 你去也帮不上忙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.32,0:16:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在战斗用机械人的战争中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.99,0:16:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人类去了也是没用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.66,0:16:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的确 或许我什么都帮不上忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.17,0:16:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.77,0:16:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.70,0:16:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还是非去不可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.65,0:16:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,史莱修
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.75,0:16:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你最初来到这个家的时候曾对我说过的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.89,0:16:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是麻幌的主人对你而言也是你的主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.93,0:16:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果这句话不是骗人的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.70,0:16:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以主人的身份命令你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.00,0:16:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要你带我去麻幌那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.30,0:16:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,0K 我的主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.04,0:16:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(接待大厅)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.92,0:17:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以为这些骗小孩的把戏有用吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.27,0:17:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.70,0:17:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.54,0:17:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为何明知打不中还要使出这种武器呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.51,0:17:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.91,0:17:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.35,0:17:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.67,0:17:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对我而言 为了赢得胜利的唯一策略
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.31,0:18:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.21,0:18:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要如何才能让这一击能够更正确的命中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.01,0:18:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美里同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.98,0:18:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停电？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.62,0:19:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,流河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.95,0:19:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,觉悟吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.67,0:20:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在一百公里范围之内发生了反物质现象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.23,0:20:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三秒后消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.40,0:20:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那道光到底是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.74,0:20:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,流河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.81,0:20:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.25,0:20:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概是麻幌所赌上的最后一击吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.02,0:20:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果出现吉数的话 我和主人等于是白跑了这一趟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.13,0:20:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要赶上啊
